ercase;color:#888;border-bottom:1px solid #eee;padding:0 0 6px">EN</h2><ul style="padding:0;margin:0;list-style:none"><li style="margin:14px 0;list-style:none"><a href="https://comprom.org/en/articles/solidarity/?utm_source=newsletter&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=2026-23" class="item-title" style="display:block;color:#ee6f57;text-decoration:none;font-size:16px;line-height:1.35;font-weight:600">Worker solidarity reaches new heights</a><div class="muted" style="margin-top:4px;font-size:13px;color:#888">2026-06-04</div></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td class="card" style="padding:8px 28px 32px;background:#fff;color:#222"><hr class="divider" style="border:none;border-top:1px solid #eee;margin:0 0 16px" /><p class="muted" style="margin:0;font-size:12px;color:#888;line-height:1.5">If you no longer wish to receive these digests, click the link above.<br /><a href="https://lists.comprom.org/unsubscribe?t=ABCDEF" class="footer-link" style="color:#ee6f57">Unsubscribe</a></p></td></tr></table></body></html>"`;

